item.dc:creator: @TabbyKiller TabbyKiller
item.description:
@TabbyKiller wrote:

lol some people are curious on how I did this so I’m just going to spit it out.

Its quite simple actually
I set off to find a topic without noobs or newcommers in it, one here and the other here I raided those topics and used this code to edit the page

javascript:document.body.contentEditable ='true';document.designMode='on'; void 0
Edited each line and each post until it was perfect, some names I had to change which took time and stuff. But if you put a lot of effort into it, it comes out good. Then I recorded it and edited a few things, zoomed in and added pictures and stuff.
then wallah, you got a MoparScape didn’t start the flame war video
